quired: Edit application Request URL Parameters: Return: A ChangeApplicationResponse (see  ChangeApplicationResponse ) object.",t:"POST /{id}/decommission"},"515":{i:0.000484698166178036,u:"../Content/api-guide/POST-id-discard.htm",a:"POST /{id}/discard Discards an application\u0027s draft revision. Resource Name: /applications/{id}/discard Permissions Required: Edit application Request URL Parameters: Return: A Status (see  Status ) object.",t:"POST /{id}/discard"},"516":{i:0.000484698166178036,u:"../Content/api-guide/POST-id-flows.htm",a:"Edits an application\u0027s flows. Resource Name: /applications/{id}/flows Permissions Required: editAllApplications createSharedFlows Request URL Parameters: Return: Error Codes: 404 (Not found) - Application wasn\u0027t found. 404 (Not found) - Flow ID wasn\u0027t found. 403 (Forbidden) - User doesn\u0027t have ...",t:"POST /{id}/flows"},"517":{i:0.000484698166178036,u:"../Content/api-guide/POST-id-flows-flowid-check_connectivity.htm",a:"Runs check connectivity on a specific flow and returns the results. Resource Name: /applications/{id}/flows/{flowID}/check_connectivity Permissions Required: Update connectivity Edit application Request URL Parameters: Return: A FlowConnectivity (see  FlowConnectivity ) object.",t:"POST /{id}/flows/{flowid}/check_connectivity"},"518":{i:0.000484698166178036,u:"../Content/api-guide/POST-id-labels.htm",a:"Edits an application\u0027s labels. Resource Name: /applications/{id}/labels Permissions Required: editAllApplications createLabels Request URL Parameters: Return: Error Codes: 404 (Not found) - Application wasn\u0027t found. 403 (Forbidden) - User doesn\u0027t have permission to edit the application. 403 ...",t:"POST /{id}/labels"},"519":{i:0.000484698166178036,u:"../Content/api-guide/POST-id-resolve.htm",a:"POST /{id}/resolve Resolves blocked flows for an application revision. Resource Name: /applications/{id}/resolve Permissions Required: Edit application Request URL Parameters: Return: A ChangeApplicationResponse (see  ChangeApplicationResponse ) object.",t:"POST /{id}/resolve"},"520":{i:0.000484698166178036,u:"../Content/api-guide/POST-new.htm",a:"Creates a new application. Resource Name: /applications/new Permissions Required: Create new application Request Body: Validation: Invalid value for existing application custom field. Existing application with the same name. No exiting contact with such email. No exiting contact role. No existing ...",t:"POST /new"},"521":{i:0.000484698166178036,u:"../Content/api-guide/POST-id-flows-new.htm",a:"Adds new flows to an application. Resource Name: /applications/{id}/flows/new Permissions Required: Edit application Create shared flow (only required when creating a shared flow) Request URL Parameters: Request Body: A list of NewFlow (see  NewFlow ) objects describing the flows to add to the ...",t:"POST /{id}/flows/new"},"522":{i:0.000484698166178036,u:"../Content/api-guide/DELETE-id-contacts.htm",a:"Removes all of an application\u0027s contacts. Resource Name: /applications/{id}/contacts Permissions Required: editAllApplications Request URL Parameters: Return: 200 - OK Error Codes: 404 (Not found) - Application wasn\u0027t found. 403 (Forbidden) - User doesn\u0027t have permission to edit the application. 403 ...",t:"DELETE /{id}/contacts"},"523":{i:0.000484698166178036,u:"../Content/api-guide/DELETE-id-custom_fields.htm",a:"Removes all custom fields for an application. Resource Name: /applications/{id}/custom_fields Permissions Required: editAllApplications Request URL Parameters: Return: 200 OK Error Codes: 404 (Not found) - Application wasn\u0027t found. 403 (Forbidden) - User doesn\u0027t have permission to edit the ...",t:"DELETE /{id}/custom_fields"},"524":{i:0.000484698166178036,u:"../Content/api-guide/DELETE-id-flows-flow_id.htm",a:"DELETE /{id}/flows/{flow_id} Deletes a flow from an application revision. Resource Name: /applications/{id}/flows/{flow_id}/ Permissions Required: Edit application Request URL Parameters: Validation: Existing application. Existing flow. Return: A Status (see  Status ) object.",t:"DELETE /{id}/flows/{flow_id}"},"525":{i:0.000484698166178036,u:"../Content/api-guide/DELETE-id-labels.htm",a:"Removes all user-defined application labels from an application. Resource Name: /applications/{id}/labels Permissions Required: editAllApplications Request URL Parameters: Return: 200 - OK Error Codes: 404 (Not found) - Application wasn\u0027t found. 403 (Forbidden) - User doesn\u0027t have permission to edit ...",t:"DELETE /{id}/labels"},"526":{i:0.000524867751358075,u:"../Content/api-guide/network_objects.htm",a:"/network_objects The following are requests for network object related resources. The base URL for network objects is /BusinessFlow/rest/v1/network_objects.",t:"/network_objects"},"527":{i:0.000484698166178036,u:"../Content/api-guide/GET_1.htm",a:"Returns a list of all network objects. Parameters: (optional) page_size - The number of results per page (Default is 1000). (optional) page_number - The page number you want to return (Default is 1). For example, if you set this parameter to 2, only the second page of objects will be returned. ...",t:"GET /"},"528":{i:0.000484698166178036,u:"../Content/api-guide/GET-id_1.htm",a:"GET /{id} Returns a network object by ID. Parameters: id - The network object revision ID. Return: NetworkObject (see  NetworkObject )",t:"GET /{id}"},"529":{i:0.000484698166178036,u:"../Content/api-guide/GET-id-applications.htm",a:"GET /{id}/applications Returns all relevant applications for the network object. Parameters: id - The network object revision ID. Return: Array of Application (see  Application )",t:"GET /{id}/applications"},"530":{i:0.000484698166178036,u:"../Content/api-guide/GET-id-vulnerabilities_1.htm",a:"GET /{id}/vulnerabilities Returns vulnerabilities for the network object. Parameters: id - The network object revision ID. Return: ObjectVulnerability (see  ObjectVulnerability )",t:"GET /{id}/vulnerabilities